{"tid":1351833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁大件事，想問下監警會去左邊","createTime":"2019-07-22T16:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T10:19:55.000Z","uid":114801,"like":87,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"26b8402a3ad1f1ac0af6138a89a7d933a355f78f","tid":1351833,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"明明之前612都有出黎扮中立<br />\n<br />\n推到佢老母西出黎開記招<br />\n<br />\n想記者當場問下：<br />\n1. 監警會負責監警，你有無權力去傳召班牛屎佬做證人？<br />\n2. 上環有恐怖分子冒警開左三十幾槍，有撚無搞撚錯，<br />\n3. 612盧偉聰話數發布袋彈，果陣仲點算緊，請問數左一個幾月，數完未"},{"pid":"9ce65ce4717aa0152eb0b46a05c1a23a665055b5","tid":1351833,"uid":114801,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:34:34.000Z","msg":"推到佢老母西聽日最遲5點前出黎開記招<br />\n<br />\n我地要趁民情洶湧，當眾踢爆呢隻紙老虎"},{"pid":"a51085931657a9947363f3c02fd7642a3187b188","tid":1351833,"uid":8007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"推 我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"4869186349955d78358dfed4fd0fdf5c3c7edf00","tid":1351833,"uid":125380,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:36:23.000Z","msg":"仲信監警會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82df92abf14aa0ed3db9a74760524941a545b6c6","tid":1351833,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:36:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe6a9db0ca560e25d80ec0f4010684e121c71f22","tid":1351833,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"9acc76e6b64cbee07a0fb7a885b96a1ae73beb50","tid":1351833,"uid":38177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4869186349955d78358dfed4fd0fdf5c3c7edf00","tid":1351833,"uid":125380,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:36:23.000Z","msg":"仲信監警會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:37:27.000Z","msg":"撕開佢嘅假面具"},{"pid":"e15c641a1689dfa2af946b19eb3bc5f931619b82","tid":1351833,"uid":279357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工 罷市</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好好利用恐懼<br />\n等林鄭自己捉蟲<br />\n以為用恐懼可以威脅香港人<br />\n我哋就用呢種威脅<br />\n去令到香港市民<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工罷市</span></span><br />\n如果成功佢哋唔會再有一次<br />\n利用呢種手段去威嚇我哋<br />\n我哋要拉商家落嚟<br />\n我哋已經動用晒<br />\n所有市民嘅資源<br />\n無論係衝擊中聯辦<br />\n定係義士用生命<br />\n去同黑警抗爭<br />\n我哋香港市民<br />\n都要陪上佢哋嘅安危<br />\n咁只有用經濟<br />\n去將呢一個極權嘅政府<br />\n從佢哋高高在上嘅位置<br />\n拉返落嚟<br />\n香港唔要一個管治型嘅政府<br />\n香港人需要嘅係<br />\n服務型嘅政府</span></span>"},{"pid":"971f610298efb52c406ac03d891599c3d9b80012","tid":1351833,"uid":114801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4869186349955d78358dfed4fd0fdf5c3c7edf00","tid":1351833,"uid":125380,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:36:23.000Z","msg":"仲信監警會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"我地要趁民情洶湧，當眾踢爆呢隻紙老虎<br />\n<br />\n大把元朗事件後 藍轉黃既人，仲覺得監警會有用<br />\n<br />\n加上今日林鄭記者會，記者們既表現，絕對可以問到佢口啞啞<br />\n<br />\n最後，全個連登都無人信監警會，但請唔好留起同溫層，歷史上大把社運輸在呢點"},{"pid":"f5b1193defaea0d35153c0c8d4ba97bdeb642020","tid":1351833,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4995cf766517824574256b3e4773c17bfb82a7","tid":1351833,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:43:20.000Z","msg":"推到佢老母西出黎開記招"},{"pid":"1cc87770f2c91f626a9b478411f16bfa9a7dee96","t